      Products & Solutions    


360° Core Services






 

Automated Traffic Safety Solutions
Brekford’s Automated Traffic Safety Enforcement Solutions offer intersection safety using photo red light and photo speed camera systems with a complete suite of program support services.
View Products






 

Parking Solutions
Many cities across the U.S. are looking to Brekford for our innovative parking solutions. Our fully customized turn-key parking management solutions offer any size municipality everything from smart meters and handheld enforcement solutions, to integrated violation management applications and collections services.
View Products






 

Vehicle Upfitting Services & Technology
Brekford provides emergency vehicle equipment integration utilizing the newest law enforcement technologies. With over 15 years of upfitting experience, Brekford’s bumper to bumper solutions will enable your vehicles to look their best, while guaranteeing minimal out of service time due to our unique, state of the art wiring harness and expert installation.
View Products






















