            Brekford Traffic Safety, Inc. is a public safety technology service provider of automated traffic safety enforcement solutions including speed, red light, and distracted driving camera systems. It also provides parking enforcement citation collections and integrator of mobile technology equipment for public safety agencies. The company products and solutions include automated traffic safety solutions, parking solutions, and vehicle up-fitting services & technology. It provides technology solutions and services to branches of the U.S. military, various federal entities and numerous public safety agencies throughout the United States. The company was founded on May 27, 1998 and is headquartered in Hanover, MD.

            
